#: ../../static_analysis.md:45
msgid "To run [Slither](https://github.com/crytic/slither#slither-the-solidity-source-analyzer) with this plugin, you need to connect Remix IDE to your filesystem with [Remixd](remixd.html).  Once Remixd is running, Slither is automatically loaded."
